{"tid":2458181,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"科興疫苗｜「三高」院舍職員覺病情穩定　今打第二針：針口都唔痛","createTime":"2021-03-23T08:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T09:00:45.000Z","uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6922fa5e28eabbce8d7e9adfe91669204949104e","tid":2458181,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:38:16.000Z","msg":"在基德護理安老院任職保健員的鍾女士，上月23日於銅鑼灣中央圖書館的接種中心接種第一劑科興疫苗。她稱，院舍負責人十分支持員工打針，當天與員工一起接種，今天二人亦分別在不同接種中心打第二針。鍾小姐選擇在天水圍天暉路體育館打第二針，她稱，打第一針後身體一切正常，可如常上班，而今天打第二針後，亦不覺得第二針反應更強烈，「連針口都唔痛，打流感針仲痛呀！」<br />\n<br />\n年屆五旬的她，在兩年前患上「三高」，即高血壓、高血脂和糖尿病，一度需注射胰島素，現時則不需再打胰島素，只需服用半顆血壓藥，空腹時血糖值約為6，而血壓的上壓大概是120至130。她自覺「三高」病情算是控制得好，亦經常監測自己的指數，相信適合打針，打第二針前並無特別諮詢醫生，「打完第一針後都好有信心，因為無咩感覺」。"},{"pid":"7976aed9e27766d776a9c7b1f7197a2f1a5826dd","tid":2458181,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:42:54.000Z","msg":"咁就得啦<br />\n有咩都一定關事<br />\n有事都係自己衰 <br />\n衰蠢 衰on9 衰抵L死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b7faacd7683ea110f31b3403ccc6088d091142","tid":2458181,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7976aed9e27766d776a9c7b1f7197a2f1a5826dd","tid":2458181,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:42:54.000Z","msg":"咁就得啦<br />\n有咩都一定關事<br />\n有事都係自己衰 <br />\n衰蠢 衰on9 衰抵L死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:43:35.000Z","msg":"咁就得啦<br />\n有咩都一定<span class=\"red\">唔</span>關事<br />\n有事都係自己衰<br />\n衰蠢 衰on9 衰抵L死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4304210d078379740fd842c8afe4836a38a575d","tid":2458181,"uid":312332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"「連針口都唔痛，打流感針仲痛呀！」<br />\n佢係咪打完已經失去部分知覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016ea93c453e3424cadab372038b7b3942d6cf7b","tid":2458181,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"過多幾日先講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b17cbd570e9ac61f0e86e670f47f43f259f8de5","tid":2458181,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"可能打咗生理鹽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb231b74f3d37fd3d9fcd6e4a97e44e2c0c4dc4","tid":2458181,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4304210d078379740fd842c8afe4836a38a575d","tid":2458181,"uid":312332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"「連針口都唔痛，打流感針仲痛呀！」<br />\n佢係咪打完已經失去部分知覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:56:33.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗，應該痛嘅覺得唔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a33dcedea98dcdb5546f9d875071749faf9c2a8","tid":2458181,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:56:42.000Z","msg":"打咗麻醉藥"},{"pid":"162b18713c2475637a8fb55a3a92ec9fb87ee904","tid":2458181,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:00:45.000Z","msg":"班支那狗究竟明唔明點解要打疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}